window.bookSummaryJSON = "In this, the sequel to <i>A Hymn Before Battle</i>, Captain Michael O'Neal and his forces on Earth prepare to hold back an impending Posleen invasion. <p> \"Thanks to alien technology and sheer guts, the Terrans on two worlds fought the Posleen to a standstill. Thank God there was a moment to catch our breath, a moment, however brief, of peace.</p> <p>\"Now, for the survivors of the Barwhon and Diess Expeditionary Forces, it was a chance to get some distance from the blood and misery of battle against the Posleen centaurs. A blessed chance to forget the screams of the dying in purple swamps and massacres under searing alien suns.\"</p>"; 
